==Graphics==
===Ryzen5 3500U===
On the T495 Ryzen 5 3500U variant, the video card does not currently work with the [https://packages.gentoo.org/packages/sys-kernel/gentoo-sources sys-kernel/gentoo-sources kernel]. Please replace it with [https://packages.gentoo.org/packages/sys-kernel/vanilla-sources sys-kernel/vanilla-sources] or a kernel >= 5.0.
====GRUB settings====
Edit/update the following line in the following file:
{{RootCmd | /etc/default/grub}} 
<pre>GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="acpi_backlight=vendor"</pre>
